VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \barc4random\s*\(|\barc4random_uniform\s*\(|\brand\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:token|key|secret|nonce|session|otp|password|salt && MISSING:SecRandomCopyBytes|CryptorRandomByte|CCRandomGenerateBytes
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects use of non-cryptographically secure random functions in security-sensitive contexts.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Insecure Random Number Generation.
